description_html: An original design with history in its roots, Kennett from the Storri Luxury Vinyl collection was named for the mushroom capital of the world. The aged, reclaimed wood-look design of Kennett comes from the farming houses, transformed by Mother Nature, used to cultivate the growth of mushrooms in Kennett Square, PA. Kennett’s design offers a variety of color tones to make a bold statement in any commercial interior setting—both on the floor and on the wall. Kennett showcases its extensive design in a 7.25” x 48” x 3mm wide plank size and is available in seven colors: Ash, Chalk, Coral, Grain, Indigo, Mica, and Timber.
